r />\n行人專用區不行人本身已經係笑話,仲要整D大媽/本地19歌手放膠音,行過都覺得嘈,而家取消左完全係普天同慶,一係你班左膠文化撚藍血大狀叫班友日日去你樓下放膠音<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">你話我想搞到香港變文化沙漠,我都係咁講</span></strong>"},{"pid":"24326f75c146cd61c6432cceb38897ec04bfe1f5","tid":687232,"uid":77905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T05:58:40.000Z","msg":"堂堂香港政府一條街都管唔好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9250b95fbb8b6944240cd5d28b8c0015f777004","tid":687232,"uid":124268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T05:58:56.000Z","msg":"老實講，要表現唔係唔得，但真係唔好再搞旺角呢度喇，去文化中心海傍啦"},{"pid":"1dc12fb816b1e0d2c971c034825c8a1a4c176d87","tid":687232,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T06:04:18.000Z","msg":"泛民不嬲離地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47249602358b6da90cf44cda8e1d9e672eab35eb","tid":687232,"uid":83228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T06:19:33.000Z","msg":"由政府規管表演？！<br />\n知唔知有幾危險"},{"pid":"8cf55bef1cb0ef9ebd5eb70a90edfbb3d678a95a","tid":687232,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T06:23:02.000Z","msg":"就係呢樣野搞到摺埋行人專用區<br />\n你咁與民為敵要保留？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd526ce0cceb5e0e8ae72d35cfd8a527927c6510","tid":687232,"uid":36820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T06:24:14.000Z","msg":"規你老母， 咪撚再搞"},{"pid":"eb6a3347d0a4304d60b7c236b260c88a59915d0e","tid":687232,"uid":5489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T07:06:44.000Z","msg":"屌你老母你係守護到街頭文化<br />\n呢幾年黎就唔洗攪到污煙漳氣 今日殺街啦<br />\n用下個閪腦啦"},{"pid":"d975abcd2c0aa0d19af0b6496d7a073c18fc29d2","tid":687232,"uid":39221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47249602358b6da90cf44cda8e1d9e672eab35eb","tid":687232,"uid":83228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T06:19:33.000Z","msg":"由政府規管表演？！<